    think="Now I have a clear picture. Let me understand what needs to be fixed:
\n\n1. **TopInfoBar** - Already uses UIText for resource icons (blocking issue f
ixed). But `setAvatar()` fallback is still a non-blocking suggestion.\n2. **Buil
dingSelector.clearSelection()** - Already calls `this.buildingList.clearSelectio
n()` (blocking issue fixed).\n3. **ConfirmationDialog tests** - Need to fix to a
ctually trigger button clicks and assert callback calls.\n4. **ConfirmationDialo
g.show(config)** - Need to handle title/message updates or document the limitati
on.\n\nLet me also check if there's an issue with the callback updating in `Conf
irmationDialog.show()`. As I analyzed, `show()` updates `this.confirmCallback` b
ut when the button is clicked, `UIDialog.confirm()` calls `this.config.onConfirm
` (UIDialog's config), not `this.confirmCallback`. So updating `confirmCallback`
in `show()` has no actual effect!\n\nThis is a real bug that should be fixed. Le
t me verify by looking at how the tests for other dialogs work.\n\nLet me also c
heck RemoveConfirmDialog and UpgradeConfirmDialog to see how they handle this.",
    encrypted=None
)
